title: Exhaust Sound: MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust on a Dodge Ram 1500
description: Listen to what happens when you install a top-quality MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust on a Dodge Ram 1500.

asset.title: MagnaFlow Dodge Ram 1500 Cat-back Exhaust System - Sound Clip
asset.description: MagnaFlow's RAM 1500 exhaust systems are available in several exit configurations for 3.8L V6 and 5.7L V8 applications and provide a deep, aggressive tone and more power. All MagnaFlow exhaust systems come with a Lifetime Warranty, and each kit includes all the necessary hardware and components for a complete, bolt-on installation. MagnaFlow products are proudly made in the USA. For more information, click here: http://bit.ly/1eygqKX
